1-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "對小說中的政府而言，「最壞情況」所指的最可能是下列何者？", "options": ["人心彼此猜疑，不再相互信任", "氣溫持續上升，民眾難以忍受", "疫情不斷惡化，人們失去求生欲", "群眾發生暴動，突破城門封鎖線"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-30", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 31, "raw_text": "31. 對小說中的政府而言，「最壞情況」所指的最可能是下列何者？\n    (A)人心彼此猜疑，不再相互信任\n    (B)氣溫持續上升，民眾難以忍受\n    (C)疫情不斷惡化，人們失去求生欲\n    (D)群眾發生暴動，突破城門封鎖線\n\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-032", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，關於美秀美術館，最不可能推論出下列何者？", "options": ["美術館坐落在山間", "對環境清潔有高度的要求", "館區的電動車由機械人駕駛", "接待中心與美術館有一段距離"], "correct_answer": 2, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-32", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 32, "raw_text": "32. 根據本文，關於美秀美術館，最不可能推論出下列何者？\n    (A)美術館坐落在山間\n    (B)對環境清潔有高度的要求\n    (C)館區的電動車由機械人駕駛\n    (D)接待中心與美術館有一段距離\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-033", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，下列何者最能體現美秀美術館的烏托邦式美學？", "options": ["工作人員親切的微笑，流露內心的祥和", "降低人為聲音的干擾，以呈現寧靜氛圍", "所有物件一律為白色，象徵藝術的純淨", "讓觀眾貼近展品，顯現人與藝術無隔閡"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-32", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 33, "raw_text": "33. 根據本文，下列何者最能體現美秀美術館的烏托邦式美學？\n    (A)工作人員親切的微笑，流露內心的祥和\n    (B)降低人為聲音的干擾，以呈現寧靜氛圍\n    (C)所有物件一律為白色，象徵藝術的純淨\n    (D)讓觀眾貼近展品，顯現人與藝術無隔閡\n\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-034", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，作者認為紙本書對一般人的獨特價值最可能是下列何者？", "options": ["紙本書才能傳承經典與藝術", "閱讀紙本書不受晝夜的限制", "紙本書可讓文字散發不同的渲染力", "城鄉數位落差因紙本書才得以彌補"], "correct_answer": 2, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-34", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 34, "raw_text": "34. 根據本文，作者認為紙本書對一般人的獨特價值最可能是下列何者？\n    (A)紙本書才能傳承經典與藝術\n    (B)閱讀紙本書不受晝夜的限制\n    (C)紙本書可讓文字散發不同的渲染力\n    (D)城鄉數位落差因紙本書才得以彌補\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-035", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "關於本文的寫作分析，下列敘述何者最恰當？", "options": ["以多面向的特質比較來強調數位資訊不如紙本", "用夜以繼日來說明紙本閱讀是數位閱讀的延續", "透過圖表的分析，陳述紙本閱讀無限發展的可能", "藉由晝夜的對照，表達紙本與數位閱讀應該並存"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-34", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 35, "raw_text": "35. 關於本文的寫作分析，下列敘述何者最恰當？\n    (A)以多面向的特質比較來強調數位資訊不如紙本\n    (B)用夜以繼日來說明紙本閱讀是數位閱讀的延續\n    (C)透過圖表的分析，陳述紙本閱讀無限發展的可能\n    (D)藉由晝夜的對照，表達紙本與數位閱讀應該並存\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-036", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "假設右圖是寓言中所指的洞穴，則根據寓言\n的內容，甲、乙、丙三處依序最可能是下列\n何者？", "options": ["被鍊著的人／營火／舉雕像的人", "被鍊著的人／舉雕像的人／營火", "舉雕像的人／營火／被鍊著的人", "舉雕像的人／被鍊著的人／營火"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-36", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": ["needs_image"], "parse_confidence": 0.85, "original_question_number": 36, "raw_text": "36. 假設右圖是寓言中所指的洞穴，則根據寓言\n    的內容，甲、乙、丙三處依序最可能是下列\n    何者？\n    (A)被鍊著的人／營火／舉雕像的人\n    (B)被鍊著的人／舉雕像的人／營火\n    (C)舉雕像的人／營火／被鍊著的人\n    (D)舉雕像的人／被鍊著的人／營火\n\n\n"}, "is_active": false, "auto_gradable": false, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-037", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "在這則寓言中，「這個走出洞穴後再回到洞內的人」最可能是象徵下列哪一種\n人？", "options": ["受迫的奴隸", "孤獨的先知", "命運的主宰", "蒙昧的愚者"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-36", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 37, "raw_text": "37. 在這則寓言中，「這個走出洞穴後再回到洞內的人」最可能是象徵下列哪一種\n    人？\n    (A)受迫的奴隸\n    (B)孤獨的先知\n    (C)命運的主宰\n    (D)蒙昧的愚者\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-038", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據這則寓言，下列何者最接近柏拉圖的想法？", "options": ["多數人相信的事未必為真", "自以為是往往會招致滅亡", "面向陽光，影子就會在你背後", "堅定信仰，心靈才能得到自由"], "correct_answer": 0, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-36", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 38, "raw_text": "38. 根據這則寓言，下列何者最接近柏拉圖的想法？\n    (A)多數人相信的事未必為真\n    (B)自以為是往往會招致滅亡\n    (C)面向陽光，影子就會在你背後\n    (D)堅定信仰，心靈才能得到自由\n\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-039", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據甲、乙兩文推論，漢文帝時各種錢幣的重量依序最可能是下列何者？", "options": ["四銖錢 ＞ 吳錢 ＞ 鄧通錢", "四銖錢 ＝ 鄧通錢 ＞ 吳錢", "吳錢 ＞ 四銖錢 ＞ 鄧通錢", "吳錢 ＞ 鄧通錢 ＝ 四銖錢"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-39", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 39, "raw_text": "39. 根據甲、乙兩文推論，漢文帝時各種錢幣的重量依序最可能是下列何者？\n    (A)四銖錢 ＞ 吳錢 ＞ 鄧通錢\n    (B)四銖錢 ＝ 鄧通錢 ＞ 吳錢\n    (C)吳錢 ＞ 四銖錢 ＞ 鄧通錢\n    (D)吳錢 ＞ 鄧通錢 ＝ 四銖錢\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-040", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據甲、乙兩文，下列敘述何者最恰當？", "options": ["鄧通與吳王同時自鑄莢錢，導致莢錢過多", "鄧通與吳王所鑄銅錢上應有「半兩」字樣", "鄧通叛逆謀反，文帝遂下令禁止私鑄銅錢", "鄧通所鑄錢布天下，故文帝賜其銅山一座"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-39", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 40, "raw_text": "40. 根據甲、乙兩文，下列敘述何者最恰當？\n    (A)鄧通與吳王同時自鑄莢錢，導致莢錢過多\n    (B)鄧通與吳王所鑄銅錢上應有「半兩」字樣\n    (C)鄧通叛逆謀反，文帝遂下令禁止私鑄銅錢\n    (D)鄧通所鑄錢布天下，故文帝賜其銅山一座\n\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-041", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，下列文句省略的主語，何者是白敏中？", "options": ["病其與賀拔惎為友", "乃密令門人申意", "悉以實告", "大怒而去"], "correct_answer": 2, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-41", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 41, "raw_text": "41. 根據本文，下列文句省略的主語，何者是白敏中？\n    (A)病其與賀拔惎為友\n    (B)乃密令門人申意\n    (C)悉以實告\n    (D)大怒而去\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-042", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，王起說：「我原只得白敏中，今當更取賀拔惎矣。」這句話的原因，\n最可能是下列何者？", "options": ["白敏中向王起推薦賀拔惎取代自己", "賀拔惎已知此次科考內幕，只好破格錄取封口", "比起白敏中的前倨後恭，賀拔惎的真誠顯得更為可貴", "白敏中把賀拔惎看得比狀元還重，可知賀拔惎有過人之處 14            試題結束"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-41", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 42, "raw_text": "42. 根據本文，王起說：「我原只得白敏中，今當更取賀拔惎矣。」這句話的原因，\n    最可能是下列何者？\n    (A)白敏中向王起推薦賀拔惎取代自己\n    (B)賀拔惎已知此次科考內幕，只好破格錄取封口\n    (C)比起白敏中的前倨後恭，賀拔惎的真誠顯得更為可貴\n    (D)白敏中把賀拔惎看得比狀元還重，可知賀拔惎有過人之處\n\n\n\n\n                     14            試題結束\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}]'::jsonb) AS t(
